title: Genasi of Air
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki
xpcost: 1

As an air [[genasi]], you gain the following benefits.

* You can hold your breath indefinitely while you're not incapacitated.
* You have [[advantage]] when resisting damage suffered from falling.
* You may cast one of the following spells: [[gust]], [[gale]], [[jump]], [[feather fall]], [[levitate]], or [[zephyr step]].
